<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied></hi> virapāṇṭiya tevaṟku yāṇṭu Añc<unclear>ā</unclear>vatu Aṟpaci tiṅkaḷ mutal ku
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṟuppu nāṭṭu vicaiyamaṅkalattu veḷḷāḷaṉ paṭattalaikaḷil neriya muventaveḷāṉ
<lb n="3"/>Aviṉāciyeṉ Āḷuṭaiyār tiruṉāki<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi>ramuṭ<unclear>ai</unclear>yāṟkuc cantiyātipam Oṉṟuk
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ku Oṭukkina Accu <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>yakki paḻañcalākaiyo<unclear>ṉ</unclear>ṟum kaikkoṇṭomikko
<lb n="5" break="no"/><unclear>yil</unclear>kā<unclear>ṇi</unclear>yuṭaiya civa<hi rend="grantha">brāhma</hi>ṇaṉ Ā<hi rend="grantha">tra</hi>ya<hi rend="grantha"> gotra</hi>ttu Āḷavanta piḻai poṟuttā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṉu māṭala<hi rend="grantha">gotra</hi>ttu Uṭaiyāṉ vetaṉāyakapaṭṭaṉum Ivviruvar kuṭa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṅko<supplied reason="omitted">ṇ</supplied>ṭu koyil pukuvāṉ cantirātittavarai viḷakkoṉṟu Erippa
